1. What kind of task should you hand off to a novice team member to complete?
Solution : A. Smaller-scale tasks that they can own from end to end

2. Which question are you most likely to ask when delegating a task to a highly experienced employee?
Solution : C. "What support do you need from me to be successful?"

3. You've decided on the deliverables and dates for your next big project. What are the final traits you use to match the responsibility to the report?
Solution : B. Ability and willingness
